      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this reliable and practical daily driver, perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been well-maintained to ensure it still offers a solid, consistent performance on the road. While it shows some honest signs of use, it remains a sturdy choice that's ready to handle your commutes with ease. Don't miss out on this great value!",
