    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is structurally sound and retains a great shine, though upon closer inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; however, there is some minor bolster wear on the driver's seat and slight fading on a few high-traffic buttons. Mechanically, the car performs reliably with no known issues, offering a smooth ride and a complete service record that demonstrates its upkeep. It is a solid, dependable vehicle that looks great but shows the honest character of a car that has been enjoyed.",
