      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been wonderfully maintained and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It runs smooth and has plenty of life left in it. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself why I've loved driving it so much!",
