    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S features the high-revving 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering power through a precise short-throw 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is optimized with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and a limited-slip differential for superior corner exit traction. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring minimal fade. Recent service includes a critical IMS bearing inspection and RMS replacement, ensuring the M97 engine's structural integrity. A mechanically tight example with a linear torque curve and communicative hydraulic steering rack, perfect for the driver who demands an analog connection to the tarmac.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Mechanically sound. Minimal interior wear.",
