    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 that perfectly captures the brand's reputation for enduring luxury. The exterior finish retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest signs of its time on the road. The interior is a non-smoker's sanctuary; the leather seats are plush and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's entry point. All electronic components, including the navigation system, power liftgate, and dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently installed a fresh set of premium tires and performed a full fluid service, ensuring this SUV is ready for its next owner. It offers a smooth, composed ride that feels sophisticated and secure.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
